Package com.activityscheduler.domain

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractDomainObject
    An Abstract class for Domain objects.
    Activity
    A domain class extending AbstractDomainObject to hold the activity information like the name, duration etc
    ActivityCatalog
    A domain class extending AbstractDomainObject to hold the activity catalog information consisting of list of activites This class consist of following domain driven design method addAllActivities() - Merge all the input activities to the catalog * addActivity() - Add the input activity to the catalog getActivityCount() - get the count of all the activities in the catalog getActivity(index) - get the activity in the catalog at the given index getLastActivity() - Get the last activity in the catalog that has the status as scheduled * extractScheduledActivities() - Extract all the activities in the catalog that has the status as scheduled hasActivities() - Return true if the catalog as atleast one activity .
    ActivitySchedule
    A domain class extending AbstractDomainObject to hold the activity schedule information for an event
    DeloitteAwayDayEventInfo
    A domain object extending EventInfo to hold the event specific information for Deloitte Digital Away day
    EventInfo
    A domain object extending AbstractDomainObject to hold the event specific information
    Team
    A domain object extending AbstractDomainObject to hold the event specific information This class consist of following domain driven design method addScheduledActivities() - Merge all the scheduled input activities to the team catalog addActivity() - Add the input activity to the team catalog getNextActivityStartTime() - Get the Start time of the next activity of the team considering the end time of the existing activity
